ldf = parseLDF('D:\\ldfe.ldf')
message = ldf.get_message_by_id(52)
bbb = b'\x00\x00\x00\x00\x00\x00'
message.decode(bbb)
diff_str = message.diff_str()
aaa = message.encode({'SIGNAL_A': 1})
diff_str = message.diff_str()
message.decode(aaa)
message.decode(bbb)
diff_str = message.diff_str()
self.assertEqual(diff_str, "{'SIGNAL_A' : 0}")
